#!/usr/bin/env perl

(require DBIx::Class::Migration::Script)
  ->run_with_options;

=head1 NAME

dbic-migration - commandline tool to create and manage your migrations

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    dbic-migration status \
      --libs="lib"
      --schema_class='MyApp::Schema' \
      --dsn='DBI:SQLite:myapp.db'

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is a script interface to L<DBIx::Class::Migration::Script>.  For now you
should review those docs and see the L<DBIx::Class::Migration::Tutorial>.

=head1 SEE ALSO

L<DBIx::Class::Migration>

=head1 AUTHOR

See L<DBIx::Class::Migration> for author information

=head1 COPYRIGHT & LICENSE

See L<DBIx::Class::Migration> for copyright and license information

=cut

